This recording is from a tour with King's X and Joe Satriani. Six Degrees Of Inner Turbulence, to my opinion one of the (many) highlights in Dream Theater's history, is fully played. The sound quality is more than acceptable I think.
I do not know if this recording is ever released as a bootleg. The recording time does not correspond with the three mentioned at Ytsecollection.com. Therefor I have no artwork for this one.

Enjoy!
